annotation_label: Merchant at seafood market falls ill. Beginning point for an increasing number of patients linked to the Hua’nan seafood market in Wuhan
Dr. Li sends message to fellow doctors warning about the outbreak

Chinese authorities quarantine Wuhan
China celebrates Lunar New Year begins. Many cities call off activities

The outbreak was declared a Public Health Emergency of International Concern
US and Italy restrict travel to China

Disease officially named COVID-19 and the virus officially named SARS-CoV-2

First US death reported by WA state

Italy puts entire country on lockdown.
